Eg. White space errors are found by your linter\
Each language has it\'92s own linter (Eg. Rubocop for Ruby)\
Code Climate for static analysis (automated code review)\
Idea: talk to folks working on creating static analyzers (eg. Andrea Orru F2\'9216) to understand what it does and doesn\'92t do\
